[00:52:39.920 --> 00:52:46.800]   And may tonight we leave forever changed.
[00:52:46.800 --> 00:52:49.880]   Not because of anything that was mentioned from this stage,
[00:52:49.880 --> 00:52:53.760]   but because you spoke.
[00:52:57.560 --> 00:52:59.560]   We love you.
